    • Method Detail

      • buildPartOfTheSuffixTrie

        void buildPartOfTheSuffixTrie(java.lang.String word)
        Build part of a Suffix Trie. Used by giving a word and which each call removing the head of the string until the string is empty. It checks if their already is part of given word as a key. If there is not all of the word is appended as a key. Otherwise, the similar letters of the key and the given will be set as the new key. The remaining letters of both the old key and the given word will be set as edges of the new key. The edges of the old key, will be added to the the corresponding parent.
        Parameters:
        word - The word to build part of the Suffix Trie of.
